s team. Your availability to respond to questions and concerns promptly amidst the other tasks and responsibilities on your plate is not lost. I really appreciate where our team is at, and the effort you've put in to help get us here. Looking forward to seeing what we can accomplish together! üôåüèª\n\n50#WHL Forum - An Only Workhuman Can Do Event!|Team, I want to express my sincere appreciation and take a moment to recognize you for the remarkable team effort that made the first-ever WHL Forum in London an extraordinary success this week. The energy and dedication you poured into planning and executing this event from garnering 591 registrations, and securing inspiring speakers, thought-leaders in Dan Health, and customers from Sanofi and bp to localizing the event creative, sourcing local entertainers with the ‚ÄúShowstoppers‚Äù, and executing a seamless and flawless logistical plan ‚Äî you were all truly exceptional.   Your passion, expertise, and collaborative spirit showed our mission and values on center stage! We created a perfect balance between knowledge-sharing and networking, leaving everyone feeling enriched and motivated - evident in how we captivated our audience and ignited their passion for creating a positive workplace culture (reinforced with our data) while allowing participants to actively engage, learn, and exchange ideas with their peers.    Your collective efforts helped support our annual business goals by creating an opportunity to engage with 72M in active pipeline across 15 opportunities, 27 customer accounts representing 280M in annual billings, 4 media interviews onsite, and 30 product demos with high-end brands like Rivian, Pearson, Lacoste, and Virgin Media. Beyond the numbers, we created a solid brand reputation in the market. You have all made a significant impact on the success of the Workhuman Live Forum, and I am grateful to have such an exceptional team by my side.   You should all feel really proud of what we accomplished this