e provided me with an opportunity to put my PR experience into action at Workhuman by connecting me with the team. I cannot express enough how appreciative I am of cross-functional teams!  Simone and Jenna, you were both so friendly and eager to hear my thoughts which left me feeling not only confident in myself but in our ability to work together. Thank you for meeting with me and for openly sharing your insight - you have tremendously helped me understand your approach to work. I am so excited to collaborate with you both!\n\n236#What a fab group of women!!|As I started to craft this award, I quickly realized - whoa, what an amazing and impressive group of female leaders!!!  As I scheduled this recent group of guest speakers to join our e-comm team meetings it never even dawned on me that you are all women, and wow, what a cool way to reflect on the success of this group and the leadership, innovation, and expertise you are bringing to the organization in your respective areas and to celebrate the success of women at Workhuman!  Thank you all for the time you took to join our recent e-comm meetings and for sharing details about your work, initiatives you're leading, ways that you're approaching the opportunities in your areas, and the results that you're driving for the company.  And beyond that, thank you for sharing notes about your career paths, about challenges you've faced and ways that you've managed through those, and how we can partner more closely together to drive success as individuals in our careers, our development, and for the company.  The team came away from each of these sessions with new learnings and opportunities to reflect and take away into their own roles and initiatives, and most importantly, inspiration from such fantastic leaders helping to take Workhuman to the next level.  Thank you and I can't wait to have each of you back later this year to share details on progress!\n\n237#Putting the Intelligence in Competitive Intel!|This award is 